									a(href='https://www.amazon.com/Art-Game-Design-Lenses-Third/dp/1138632090') Schell, Jesse. 2004. The Art of Game Design: A Book of Lenses (3rd ed.)
					

	+footer('Adam Vesecký (FIT CTU)', 'Architecture of Computer Games')
